Add 1 "Gem-Knight" card from your Deck to your hand, then you can Fusion Summon 1 "Gem-Knight" Fusion Monster from your Extra Deck, banishing monsters from your hand or your side of the field as Fusion Materials. You can only activate 1 "Absorb Fusion" per turn. You cannot Special Summon any monsters the turn you activate this card, except "Gem-Knight" monsters.
